一.授权码模式:
1,获取授权码:
http://localhost:8081/bzzauth/oauth/authorize?response_type=code&client_id=browser_app_client&redirect_uri=http://localhost:8081/bzzauth/login
2,返回:
http://localhost:8081/bzzauth/login?code=h6qnJc
3,获取access_token
http://localhost:8081/bzzauth/oauth/token?
grant_type=authorization_code
&code=h6qnJc&client_id=browser_app_client
&client_secret=browser_secret&redirect_uri=http://localhost:8081/bzzauth/login

二:用户名密码模式:
1.http://localhost:8081/bzzauth/oauth/token?grant_type=password&client_id=unity_client&client_secret=unity&username=admin&password=admin


